column5: This annual event starts this Friday, anyone planning on going? If so please drop by the "EVERYTHING you wanted to know about FISHING but were afraid 2 ask..." exhibit which will be located right at the main entrance! Check out this new educational showcase, would love your feedback and in return, if you mention this board, I'll give you a nice prize! There will also be some great FREE seminars to catch as well while you're there! Hope to see you all there!
After schools being closed and sports events canceled or postponed, I'm wondering why anyone would want to take a chance.
Large events are being cancelled one after the other...  2 meters please.
Peterborough just got cancelled til May 31st
